title: Nicole Byer Returns
description:
Comedian Nicole Byer feels giddy about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.


 

Nicole returns to chat with Conan about being loved by kids, the wisdom of John Cena, and being horny for love. Later, Conan and his team attempt to hold it together while Sona is away on her book tour.



 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.


 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
